The first Turkish family with Rotor syndrome diagnosed at the molecular level.

Gümüş E(1), Karaca M(2), Deveci U(3), Jirsa M(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Medical Genetics, Harran University Faculty of Medicine, 
Şanlıurfa, Turkey.
