Prioritized Research for the Prevention, Treatment, and Reversal of Chronic 
Disease: Recommendations From the Lifestyle Medicine Research Summit.

Vodovotz Y(1), Barnard N(2), Hu FB(3), Jakicic J(4), Lianov L(5), Loveland D(6), 
Buysse D(7), Szigethy E(7), Finkel T(8), Sowa G(9), Verschure P(10), Williams 
